### Register a citizen user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Manish Thakur",
  "email": "manish@test.com",
  "password": "test1234",
  "role": "citizen",
  "bloodGroup": "B+",
  "age": 21
}

### Register a volunteer
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
