{
  "name": "Arjun Mehta",
  "email": "arjun@test.com",
  "password": "test1234",
  "role": "volunteer"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "manish@test.com",
  "password": "test1234"
}